{
  "text": "Scheme 5. The ground-state (4) and the first-excited state (4a) conformers of sodiated 4-thiouracil Figure 6 . Plot of the binding free energy, -ΔG o , at 298 K for the first (•) and second (○) water molecule versus corresponding sodium ion affinity of uracil and thiouracils. For U, 2-SU, and 6Me2SU, the calculated sodium ion affinity values are taken from Reference [CITATION_1] ; for 4SU from Reference [CITATION_2] ; see Table 2 ",
